Installation
============

Re-write rules
**************

eZYUI extension require correct re-write rule in order to load necessary files
from the file system. This is required only when INI setting

Virtual-Host setup
------------------

Add to your Virtual-Host setup following line:

``^/extension/[^/]+/design/[^/]+/(stylesheets|flash|images|lib|javascripts?)/.* - [L]``